[The avian influenza H7N9 virus outbreak is maintaining its characteristic features and can be expected to continue at least for the duration of the normal 'seasonal' winter epidemic period. It seems inevitable that the outbreak may extend beyond the borders of mainland China, unless there is more stringent control of the movement of poultry in border regions. - Mod.CP

Maps of China can be seen at http://www.sacu.org/maps/provmap.png and http://healthmap.org/r/1zaU. - Sr.Tech.Ed.MJ]
